import React from 'react';

class Register extends React.Component {

    render() {
        return <form className="form_register">
            <label>
                Name
                <input type="text"/>
            </label>
            <label>
                Email
                <input type="email"/>
            </label>
            <label>
                Password
                <input type="password"/>
            </label>
            <label>
                Birthdate
                <input/>
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="Submit" value="Submit"/>
            </label>
        </form>;
    }
}

export default Register;
